      "acceptanceCriteria": "CFD solver must have documented version control, regression test suite, and traceable release notes consistent with MRL 2 requirements.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 used under institutional software QA protocol. Version-controlled solver release with documented regression test results. Software qualification record SQR-2023R2 on file. Achieved level meets required level for MRL 2."
    },
    {
