      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must demonstrate correct implementation of governing equations via method-of-manufactured-solutions or equivalent benchmark for incompressible viscous flow.",
      "rationale": "ANSYS Fluent 2023R2 verified against ASME V&V 20 benchmark cases for incompressible Navier-Stokes. Lid-driven cavity and backward-facing step benchmarks reproduced within solver tolerance. Code verification documentation provided by vendor and independently confirmed."
    },
    {
